analysis.reasoning: Overall B presents slightly better relevance to the query. B surfaces the actual adult sit-baths (including the white/200L-style product) higher in the grid and places fewer small accessory items before main product variants. Top results in B are more clearly product listings (tubs) rather than accessories, so users searching specifically for a white 200L sit-bath get more relevant results sooner. Both pages suffer from repeated listings of the same product images, but B orders the core tubs slightly more prominently and consistently, improving immediate user value.
